xyz.swatt.data_mapping

Class SqlPojoMapping<T extends DataMapping>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.data_mapping.SqlPojoMapping<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataMapping

    @LogMethods
public class SqlPojoMapping<T extends DataMapping>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataMapping

    Use this class to validate that two different Columns in two different SqlPojos are equal.

    Note: T is the DataMapping class to use to back this one. Supported Options:

    • BigDecimalMapping - To be used if the SqlPojo's Column's Values are in BigDecimal format
    • LocalDateTimeMapping
    • LongMapping
    • StringMapping
    • ObjectMapping

    Note: This class is used instead of direct comparison, to simplify large batches of comparisons, and to provide common functionality.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)
